.DT
help
Discworld player help
help

Name
.SI 5
help - The help system
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
help [command]
help <spell>
help <command>
help <object>
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This command can be used to get help on commands, spells or objects.
If you go help by itself it will give you a list of the general help
available to you.  All spells and commands should also have their own
help which you can read.  Some objects will also have help and going
help <object> should give you this help.

To get help explicately on a spell or command assuming they clash with
something you can put a spell and command in front of the name.  ie
'help spell calm'.
.EP

Example
.SI 5
> help
Available options are

General:
   soul   alias  idea

Commands:
   look   kill   get   put   drop   stop
> help spell calm
<Help on calm deleted>
.EI

See also
.SI 5
none.
.EI
